解决方案 添加 cache  ` private static Map<String,List<String>> cacheEvaluateMap=new HashMap<>();

    /**
     * Split and evaluate inline expression.
     *
     * @return result list
     */
    public List<String> evaluate() {
        if (null == inlineExpression) {
            return Collections.emptyList();
        }
        List<String> cacheEvaluate=cacheEvaluateMap.get(inlineExpression);
        if(cacheEvaluate!=null){
            return cacheEvaluate;
        }
        cacheEvaluate= flatten(evaluate(split()));
        cacheEvaluateMap.put(inlineExpression,cacheEvaluate);
        return cacheEvaluate;
    }`

我使用了官网的JPA示例进行了修改，发现问题同样存在，使用JPA更新对象时，能否像insert一样，参数中包含了分表字段即可定位到具体的表，而不是遍历所有表。

代码如下：
`
@Repository
@Transactional
public class OrderItemRepositoryImpl implements OrderItemRepository {
    
    @PersistenceContext
    private EntityManager entityManager;
    
    @Override
    public Long insert(final OrderItem orderItem) {
        entityManager.persist(orderItem);
        return orderItem.getOrderItemId();
    }
    
    @Override
    public void delete(final Long orderItemId) {
        Query query = entityManager.createQuery("DELETE FROM OrderItem i WHERE i.orderItemId = ?1 AND i.userId = 51");
        query.setParameter(1, orderItemId);
        query.executeUpdate();
    }
    
    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
    @Override
    public List<OrderItem> selectAll() {
        return (List<OrderItem>) entityManager.createQuery("SELECT i FROM Order o, OrderItem i WHERE o.orderId = i.orderId").getResultList();
    }

    @Override
    public void update(OrderItem orderItem) {
        //使用对象更新操作，会遍历所有表，而不是像insert一样，根据参数中包含的分表字段进行定位具体的表
        orderItem.setUserId(12);
        entityManager.merge(orderItem);
    }

    @Override
    public OrderItem get(Long orderItemId) {
        return null;  //To change body of implemented methods use File | Settings | File Templates.
    }
}`
